            "headline": "Director, Product Marketing | MBA in Marketing & Strategy",
            "summary": "As the Global Head of VMware Cloud Product Marketing, Harsh Singh leads the go-to-market strategy and execution for VMware's multi-cloud portfolio, driving growth and customer adoption across regions and segments. He also serves as an Executive at the CMO Council, an Advisory Council at Harvard Business Review, an Angel Investor at several startups, and an Advisor at several companies, leveraging his extensive experience and network in the technology industry.\n\nHarsh Singh is a data-driven and empathetic marketing leader passionate about simplicity, collaboration, and mutual growth. He has a Master of Business Administration from the University of Michigan - Stephen M. Ross School of Business, focusing on Marketing and Strategy, and a Bachelor of Technology in Electrical and Electronics Engineering from the Indian Institute of Technology, Delhi. He combines his analytical acumen, strategic vision, and storytelling skills to craft compelling narratives, understand customer needs, and bridge organizational and cultural differences. He excels in building and empowering diverse teams, guiding them through complexity and change, and enabling them to realize their potential and deliver remarkable results.",
